description: Alterations to Plots A10 and A11 of planning permission 2011/1815 dated 30th March 2012 including consolidation of affordable housing into Plot A11, alterations to internal layout and elevations, alterations to accommodation mix and introduction of glazed roof structure to A10 to be treated as non-material amendment to planning permission 2011/1815 dated 30th March 2012 for demolition of all existing buildings and construction of a mixed use redevelopment to provide residential, commercial, hotel, community and assembly and leisure uses and associated parking, energy centres and new public amenity space.
